May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike, outdoors and text that says 'LECAS OIL ANLUK alexmartin_ 26 help, it's been that kind year. Had small crash Jnadi the 2nd moto last weekend and reinjured the wrist hurt Supercross. I've been working very hard come back from numerous injury's this year, out the reality I've missed to seat time have been more focused rehab and physica therapy this summer than actual training tough decision the doing what love representing my sponsors, this point decided be done racing for the summer ndlet all injuries heal properly.
